{
  "stem": "1550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there was still a lot of horse traffic in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, the beer and ice was delivered by horse-drawn traffic in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And many people have still had chickens you know, in the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had chicken farms and my father had a business supplying those people with grain and hay and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, in March, the German army still had a lot of horses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So on March the 12th or the 13th, a few days after the Germans arrived, a German sergeant or something arrived at my father's store.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came in and said, is this a Jewish store?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father said yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said to him, look, we need all kinds of stuff for our horses and you have to deliver this and this and this and this all to this address at a certain barracks.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you'll get paid for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father of course loaded it all up and he had it all delivered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So after that, my father thought if that goes on like this, in about another week or so, all my, my store will be gone.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So what he did, he went to one of his Christian competitors and said, listen, I'm prepared to sell you my entire inventory at rock bottom-- at a discount.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You want to take it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well he said yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my father sold him the whole stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was out of business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my father was out of business within a week after the-- within a week after the Nazis had arrived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So after that, we realized that we had to leave because there's no way staying-- no sense staying here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You can't get another job or a business under those circumstances.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
